			<h3>Vacuum Insulation</h3>
			<p>The entire Hydro Flask line is vacuum insulated, which means there is an absence os matter between the two stainless steel walls. Since there is no matter, the temperature outside of the flask has a difficult time affecting the temperature of the contents inside the flask.</p>
